Class GenericCallMetaDataProvider

java.lang.Object
  org.springframework.jdbc.core.metadata.GenericCallMetaDataProvider
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
Db2CallMetaDataProvider, DerbyCallMetaDataProvider, OracleCallMetaDataProvider, SqlServerCallMetaDataProvider, SybaseCallMetaDataProvider
public class GenericCallMetaDataProvider
extends Object
implements CallMetaDataProvider

Generic implementation for the CallMetaDataProvider interface. This class can be extended to provide database specific behavior.

Since:
2.5
Author:
Thomas Risberg
